        "start": 191.283,
        "end": 203.984
      },
      {
        "segment": "Our physical body complex covering, which you call the integument, had a golden luster.",
        "start_offset": 728,
        "end_offset": 815,
        "start": 207.704,
        "end": 227.104
      },
      {
        "segment": "In this form we decided to come among your peoples.",
        "start_offset": 816,
        "end_offset": 867,
        "start": 230.164,
        "end": 243.724
      },
      {
        "segment": "Your peoples at that time were much unlike us in physical appearance, as you might call it.",
        "start_offset": 868,
        "end_offset": 959,
        "start": 246.804,
        "end": 268.745
      },
      {
        "segment": "We, thus, did not mix well with the population and were obviously other than they.",
        "start_offset": 960,
        "end_offset": 1042,
        "start": 272.205,
        "end": 296.805
      },
      {
